%h2 You have chosen to hide these requests
- for hidden_request in @hidden_requests
  = hidden_request.request.household
  = link_to 'x', {:controller => 'settings', :action => 'destroy', :id => hidden_request.id}, :confirm => 'Are you sure?', :method => :delete
  %br

%h2 You have chosen to hide requests from these households
-for hidden_household_request in @hidden_household_requests
  = find_hidden_household(hidden_household_request)
  = link_to 'x', {:controller => 'settings', :action => 'destroy', :id => hidden_household_request.id}, :confirm => 'Are you sure?', :method => :delete
  %br